Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.66,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.66,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.37,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.37,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:07.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:07.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been odd lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, but it doesn't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:41.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:45.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Things I need to do... as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There should've been a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:53.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My nose hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:02:00.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I feel foggy because of the allergies I started having this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My sight grows fuzzy from the tearing eyes and running nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come to, I'm always thinking about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:15.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the cherry blossom petals are\Nconstantly falling in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:19.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it feels like I'm rewinding and watching\Nthe same video over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:26.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Professor Tange is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How heart-breaking... all because he became affiliated with Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he repeating the year again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally going to be in the same year as Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:58.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll finally see the birth of a legendary eighth grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is the very person who made Professor like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he pouring Professor some sake—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.67,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(153,241,182,599)\frz-71\shad0\fs44\b0\fsp1\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4D4879&\3c&HAAB5B1&}Morita Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\fnTimes New Roman\frz-72\shad0\fs46\b0\pos(479,258)\c&HDBE0DD&\3c&H62669D&}Morita{\c&HBF7EBB&\3c&H5A5D91&}'s {\c&HD7DED9&\3c&H69B186&}Zundoko {\c&HB770A9&\3c&H69B186&}bushi {\3c&H5A5D91&\c&HB770A9&}of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:21.64,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Zundoko-bushi:{\be1\3c&H000000&} a popular Japanese song based on a WWII\Nnaval ballad and remade several times over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:27.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The final train comes in like it does every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It shakes the red lanterns downstairs as it passes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:35.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's singing naturally and blending into some strangers' group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it looks like everyone was waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He already has speakers and spotlights\Nset up, and even made his own flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he couldn't finish his graduate thesis on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he's doing it again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fifth time I've seen his Gian recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.42,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Gian: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a boy from Doraemon. He can't sing at\Nall but makes everyone listen to his singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are some provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, what about your company's cherry blossom\Nviewing? I heard you were appointed the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:10.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was yesterday, but it turned into a mahjong\Ntournament due to the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really caught me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was staking out a spot when it started pouring all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's switch things over to a mahjong tournament, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a reservation at Tachikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You're spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a flower petal in your cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you drink it along with the petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:14.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a toast with everyone from the shopping\Ndistrict soon, so I need to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayu! It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:23.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the further prosperity of the Hamadayama\Nshopping district! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.10,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad1\bord0\c&FFFFFF&\b1\be1\bord0.1\fnTimesNewRoman\fscx65\fs48\fad(700,0)\3c&H938396&}And 25 minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with his fancy glasses? That poser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:38.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Ayu! She has absolutely no taste in good men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so good about that four-eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\fs32\fscx80\fsp1\c&H969C9F&\3c&HEFF6F7&\pos(293,33)}Fish Market, third generation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\fs32\fscx80\fsp1\c&H969C9F&\3c&HEFF6F7&\pos(115,222)}Ramen Restaurant\Nthird generation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\fs32\fscx80\fsp1\c&H969C9F&\3c&HEFF6F7&\pos(481,248)}Sushi Restaurant\Nthird generation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\fs32\fscx80\fsp1\c&H969C9F&\3c&HEFF6F7&\pos(734,24)}Butcher, third generation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\fs32\fscx80\fsp1\c&H969C9F&\3c&HEFF6F7&\pos(612,306)}Electronics Store\Nthird generation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that man has no taste in good women, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:51.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though our beloved Ayu-sama thinks about him so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:56.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's infatuated with some other woman who won't\Neven look his way and is essentially a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he thinking? It's absolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you spendthrift who doesn't even fear God...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\fs52\fscx70\fsp0.5\c&H969C9F&\3c&HEFF6F7&\pos(212,264)}Bread Store, third generation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can respect his spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, Ippei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her cute face as she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:14.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And her beautiful legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And her pristine heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed a bit since she was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how she's hurting herself over an unrequited love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:28.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that man doesn't flinch, even while\Nbeing showered by Ayu-sama's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:36.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit of that four-eyes for not just gobbling her up, even after\Nhaving this cuteness in front of him for four years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ippei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, Ippei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected from the chair of\Nthe Third Generation Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To that four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what a bother. I'm totally popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! A mountain of tributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be true. A big pile of fan letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand society anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:11.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What will become of Japan if a man like this is praised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Mouse No. 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:14.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what the heck? And I was going\Nto let her join the Chibi-Hamus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.25,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Chibi-Hamus (Little Hamsters): {\be1\3c&H000000&}a reference to Mini Moni, a subgroup\Nof Morning Musume consisting of the youngest members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:26.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, did you by chance dote on a dog or cat and\Ncause it to become neurotic when you were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, all of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:50.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I won't let you see her when she's wearing this outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, I'm kinda hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I start eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:00.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they rainbow riceballs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This green riceball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it had beefsteak plant, but it's actually mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:11.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgu—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:15.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan hasn't been lively lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since around the time she went out with Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened between the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she stopped putting that broach with the little bird on her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Morita-san has noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-sensei, where's Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I asked her to buy me a boxed meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she should've been back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the store is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:10.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you Hagusuke, Chibi Hamus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:37.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well? Yeah? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some sunflower seeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! A rolled mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:36.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! You're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei! Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I like cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:03.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... why do I feel relieved when they all scatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:09.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm released from that melancholy\Nfeeling of lamenting their scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you seem to be pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.54,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.5\be1\frz-8\fs15\move(500,427,500,507)\c&H7CB9C3&}Movie\NSociety
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.00,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1.0\be1\c&H47514F&\frz-8\fs13\b1\move(494,359,494,501)\3c&HAEB2B0&}Let's be\Npopular
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.62,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)\shad0\bord1.2\be1\c&H5D77A2&\frz-10\fs13\b1\move(433,297,433,525)\3c&HD7E3E1&}Come to the\NTennis Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H0F2256&\frz11\fs13\b1\move(710,401,710,515)}Railroad\NMania\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all flyers for attracting new freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, want to join the Tennis Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You like light music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp1\fscx80\b0\fs44\fad(0,500)\pos(162,336)\c&H80AEBB&\3c&HEAFCFF&}Second year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp1\fscx80\b0\fs44\fad(0,500)\c&H80AEBB&\3c&HEAFCFF&\pos(732,430)}Second year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm already a fourth-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takemoto, want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, where's Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And her fever is still at 37.4°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:54.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this really isn't anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before a school trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:06.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...right before the awards ceremony for an art exhibit,\Nor the day of her interview for an art magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:09.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's something like a wisdom fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisdom fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure is taking a while this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she won't tell me anything. I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:24.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, the pace of her work has been slowing down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:28.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, I couldn't keep up no matter how\Nmany new canvases I got for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:34.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan seems to have been feeling down lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I have no idea what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do for her if I don't know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:47.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My little princess's face makes it seem like\Nshe's going to sleep for a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like the Sleeping Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping Beauty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she's not going to wake up unless\Nshe gets that... you know, a prince's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a prince's ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.01,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\3c&H000000&}The kanji is actually for the fish {\3c&H635514&\be0}"Kisu"{\be1\3c&H000000&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fad(500,0)\fs21\fsp-1\c&H6A6665&\pos(300,51)}Wisdom fever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fad(500,0)\fsp-1\fs21\c&H6A6665&\pos(421,32)}Deduction
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\shad0\bord0\fad(500,0)\b1\fs21\pos(542,23)\c&H6A6665&}Culprit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fad(500,0)\fsp-1\fs21\c&H6A6665&\pos(241,158)}laid up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\shad0\bord0\fad(500,0)\fsp-1\fs21\c&H6A6665&\pos(515,133)}Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fad(500,0)\b1\fs22\c&H6A6665&\pos(398,144)\3c&HE3E2E5&}a kiss from\Na prince
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:14.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... I know, so please... put away that bat with nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:16.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, your diagram is in a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:24.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when Hagu went shopping with Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:29.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She came back that day and dejectedly told me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.75,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't tell him that she wanted to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't even eat in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she didn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she likes him, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:14:02.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was simply happy that she could be herself in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:08.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The way she happily ate her flan in front of me was adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:14.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Being so nervous that even swallowing becomes\Ndifficult when you're with that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's called love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've been in love all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:38.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is odd. You're home early, Mayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, depends on how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:46.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. So instead of coming home in the morning after\Nan all-nighter at work, you came back in the evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, I'm sleepy but hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I should just go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I haven't eaten anything since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.30,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. His judgment ability is noticeably impaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.30,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\be1\shad0\3c&HD4CFF4&\fs32\pos(185,97)\c&HA981CA&}Judgment Ability
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.30,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\shad0\3c&HD4CFF4&\fs32\be1\pos(679,83)\c&HB28B78&}Currently dropping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right. I'll go boil some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:04.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:10.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:17.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enter your access number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enter the keyword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enter your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:33.75,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san's room — the one that nobody could see the inside of?!\NThe one that has been called the "black hole" of this apartment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.38,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's bypassing the SASF security at an amazing speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Password accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Access granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.34,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:49.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Morita-san himself rarely gets access on his first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get into my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:52.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3.5\shad0\fnTahoma\fscx45\fsp4\fs50\fad(500,0)\move(141,287,227,307)\c&H6179BE&\3c&H2E3949&}Mayama's Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:56.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming voice. Please state your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:56.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Me" isn't understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru! It's Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:00.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:02.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me! I'm in a hurry here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna break you, stupid machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Kaoru-san, please recite\Nyour three favorite tongue twisters—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.62,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's forcing his way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.54,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.84,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Passport...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:23.97,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it to Narita in 50 minutes at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:29.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:32.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? Don't take your eyes off that idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have him getting lost on top of what's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto just left on a motorcycle with the passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also head your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.36,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Passport...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.03,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Narita!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:51.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:54.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... is Morita-san going somewhere? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? For work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:16:59.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Los Angeles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:01.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,America?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When is he coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe in half a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:06.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:09.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me. I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting into someone's car just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Morita-san's junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I promised to see him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seatbelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:35.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. We're stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:06.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it to him on time? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so good over here. I'm stuck at\Nthe entrance due to an inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:11.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a wasted effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never got his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:44.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it! Why are you always being so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He has everything I want in the palm of his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he doesn't even bother hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose all of them like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I was in a hurry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.13,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\shad0\be1\b0\fnArial Black\fscx80\fscx60\fs44\frx354\fry344\frz-12\fsp-1\c&H436866&\3c&H221B21&\pos(484,286)}Idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.30,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\shad0\be1\b0\fnArial Black\fscx80\fscx60\fs44\frx354\fry344\frz-5\fsp-1\c&H436866&\3c&H221B21&\pos(502,294)}Idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How am I going to get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done seeing him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.14,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He was watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, shall we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're riding with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.11,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I've seen him somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.03,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, he looks just like him when I take a closer look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:39.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, are you perhaps Morita-san's older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look a lot like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't compare me to that wild, money-hungry man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. So you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm his older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:55.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you took away his ability to make money,\Nhe'd just be a paleolithic caveman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're short on time, so I'll speed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch out... for your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.41,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything, he drove me to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.32,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.03,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1\be1\frz28\i1\fs14\pos(376,352)\3c&H6559EF&\c&H110E1F&}Normal\NHighway\NExpress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.03,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\shad0\bord0\frz30\fs16\pos(470,301)\c&H6659DA&}Morita Taxi (personal)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.03,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\shad0\bord0\fsp-1\frz25\fs24\pos(554,194)\c&H7A74F1&}yen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:24.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 47,200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.50,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are alike! Is it the DNA?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:32.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got in without your permission\Nand even had you drive me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only have... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep taking good care of Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:54.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In his address book, Shinobu wrote "Mayama the\Nintellectual" and "Takemoto the Shiba dog."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When will Morita-san be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't tell you exactly when.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:09.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But considering the amount of work he accepted,\Nhe shouldn't be able to come back so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want him to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
