Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
